     2	"""MCP surface. The capability model maps to each tool's INPUT schema only.
     3	A catalogued CLI's output_types are result *content*, NOT a declared tool
     4	outputSchema (category-error fix). Transport is Streamable HTTP, mounted on the
     5	same ASGI app as REST+A2A; auth composes with the A2A bearer."""
